[Name] Perl-File-Spec
[Summary] Portably perform operations on file names
[Description] The File::Spec distribution provides a group of modules
for working with paths and file specs across platforms. It also
includes Cwd. 
Please note that the modules from this package are already included in
perl 
This is provided for people that needs the newer versions of
File::Spec from CPAN.
